public class BirthDeathSerialSkylineModel
extends SpeciationModel

Beginning of tree prior for birth-death + serial sampling + extant sample proportion. More Tanja magic...

log: 25 Mar 2011, Denise: added int i (index) for the Variables that change over time such as the methods p0(..), q(..); fixed some formulas (old versions commented out) unclear marked with todo
